                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170416-37-off200 t18170416-37-cd201"></join>, two silver candlesticks, value 5l.; one silver snuffers-stand, value 10s. 6d.; and one pair of snuffers, value 5s., the property of 
                     
